{"tid":794670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[oncc] 南亞村藏污納垢　記者訪攝遭村民威嚇掟爛攝錄機","createTime":"2018-08-26T12:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T12:51:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"703598964e5579a54f2af9fb9df37f1acef2852c","tid":794670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:27:17.000Z","msg":"已淪黑幫兵竇、槍械庫及「吸毒特區」的深水埗通州街橋底「南亞村」，多年來罪惡叢生藏污納垢，惟政府清拆「齋噏」，多個部門互相卸責唔敢拆，令這治安毒瘤持續發酵。今早(26日)8時許，《東網》記者巡村採訪，一名戴鴨舌帽、背着棕色斜孭袋的男村民，乍見記者舉機拍攝，即惡形惡相衝前，以粗言穢語指罵記者：「Ｘ你ＸＸ臭Ｘ！你唔好咁影呀喇！你影咩呀影！你影咩呀影！」<br />\n<br />\n記者表示上址橋底為公眾地方，有權採訪拍攝，惟對方卻質問記者：「有冇問過人？有冇問過我哋？有冇批准？總之影到我屋企就唔得！」其後他又繼續指罵：「你再影我掟爛你部機！」記者見人身安全受威脅，表明會報警處理。該村民未予理會：「你影我我就一定掟爛佢（攝錄機）！我一定打爛！」又稱：「人到最低點，驚你啲咩？」<br />\n<br />\n期間，有至少6名村民輪流上前助拳起哄，一名赤膊男村民則上前調停，而揚言要掟爛記者攝錄機的男村民，最後掉頭漸行漸遠，返回橋底一間木板屋內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180826/photo/bkn-20180826170219170-0826_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180826192914\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180826%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180826170219170-0826_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180826192914&h=dccc47df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180826/bkn-20180826170219170-0826_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180826%2Fbkn-20180826170219170-0826_00822_001.html&d=7xb6q4ue7qxBCk5RO%2FwKuwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=00283208\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180826/bkn-20180826170219170-0826_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"48c67a352c19ccdcc7753e0deafd53c7703c8efe","tid":794670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"必誅"},{"pid":"b1929f8c0b5ee18a241b22c4aa61354935e2917a","tid":794670,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"老貓屋企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b578ee3087f6ad9c9d6d29ca4e0de9bcefa0419","tid":794670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"南蝗Vs東方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c25f69f1398df5b664539cb56e09c233dd4bce","tid":794670,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"人到最底點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add8131ac854b284845c2ba72405a1f7325a4e29","tid":794670,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44c25f69f1398df5b664539cb56e09c233dd4bce","tid":794670,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"人到最底點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"咁不如入去坐 有飯食 有倉住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42199a7c4e2ac75f8a34c32f39be171b545c4a50","tid":794670,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"呢個世界窮人最惡，因為佢地都爛命一條冇野輸"},{"pid":"266a403b8d26704ba0369531e11b8c0660566ee5","tid":794670,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"召喚關sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}